net.bytebuddy.description.field

Interface FieldDescription

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AnnotatedCodeElement, ByteCodeElement, DeclaredInType, ModifierReviewable, NamedElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FieldDescription.AbstractFieldDescription, FieldDescription.ForLoadedField, FieldDescription.Latent, InstrumentedType.AbstractBase.FieldToken

    public interface FieldDescription
extends ByteCodeElement
    Implementations of this interface describe a Java field. Implementations of this interface must provide meaningful equal(Object) and hashCode() implementations.
